            <li>
              Indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages
            </li>
            <li>Loss of profits, revenue, data, or business opportunities</li>
            <li>Costs of procurement of substitute services</li>
            <li>
              Damages arising from your use or inability to use the services
            </li>
            <li>Third-party claims against you</li>
            <li>Issues caused by factors beyond my reasonable control</li>
          </ul>

